{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0001","text":"但願你別回去 這一生就伴我走 還想開口","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["挽留","承諾","渴望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["別回去","伴我走","開口"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,5,2,0,4,5,3,3,2,2,5,9,0,9,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","jyun6","nei5","bit6","wui4","heoi3","ze5","jat1","sang1","zau6","bun6","ngo5","zau2","waan4","soeng2","hoi1","hau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但願","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你別","pos":"X"},{"text":"回去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"一生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"伴","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"走","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"開口","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"祈使句，表達強烈挽留的願望，語氣懇切。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0002","text":"而明白不能祈求 只好再吻着你手","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["無奈","現實","懇求"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["不能","祈求","吻","手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,3,0,0,0,9,9,4,5,2,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji4","ming4","baak6","bat1","nang4","kei4","kau4","zi2","hou2","zoi3","man5","zoek6","nei5","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"明白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不能","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"祈求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"只好","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"手","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"轉折句，表達對現實的無奈和對不可能的祈求。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0003","text":"若就當是朋友 愛火偏又沒法收 狂戀一刻","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["友情","愛情","掙扎"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["朋友","愛火","沒法收","狂戀"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,0,5,4,9,3,2,2,4,3,0,9,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","zau6","si6","pang4","jau5","oi3","fo2","pin1","jau6","mut6","faat3","sau1","kwong4","lyun2","jat1","hak1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"當","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"朋友","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"愛火","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"偏","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒法","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"收","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"狂戀","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一刻","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"假設句，將關係比喻為朋友，但內心愛火難以抑制。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0004","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0004","text":"情人便不能停留 轉身去歸他所有","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["失去","無奈","現實"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["情人","不能","停留","歸","所有"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,3,0,0,0,9,3,4,3,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cing4","jan4","bin6","bat1","nang4","ting4","lau4","zyun2","san1","heoi3","gwai1","taa1","so2","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"情人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不能","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"停留","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"轉身","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"歸","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"所有","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"判斷句，描述情人關係無法維持的現實。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0005","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0005","text":"愛不到要偷 才明瞭我與你永遠也偷不夠","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["偷情","慾望","不滿足"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["愛不到","偷","永遠","偷不夠"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,3,4,4,3,0,0,0,5,5,5,5,5,5,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["oi3","bat1","dou3","jiu3","tau1","coi4","ming4","liu4","ngo5","jyu5","nei5","wing5","jyun5","jaa5","tau1","bat1","gau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"偷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"才","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"明","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"與","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"永遠","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"偷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不夠","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"判斷句，點出「偷」的行為，並表達慾望的永不滿足。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0006","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0006","text":"像被下了咒 明明愛你 明明要你 偏偏要放開手","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["掙扎","矛盾","痛苦"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["下咒","明明愛","明明要","放開手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,5,4,0,0,4,5,0,0,4,5,3,3,4,4,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoeng6","bei6","haa6","liu5","zau3","ming4","ming4","oi3","nei5","ming4","ming4","jiu3","nei5","pin1","pin1","jiu3","fong3","hoi1","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"被","pos":"PART"},{"text":"下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"咒","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"明明","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"明明","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"偏偏","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"放開手","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"比喻句，將情況比作被下咒，強調內心的矛盾與痛苦。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0007","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0007","text":"我不想再偷 然而如不偷 一刻都不可擁有","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["掙扎","佔有","痛苦"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["不想","偷","不可","擁有"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,9,4,3,0,0,0,3,3,3,3,3,3,9,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","bat1","soeng2","zoi3","tau1","jin4","ji4","jyu4","bat1","tau1","jat1","hak1","dou1","bat1","ho2","jung2","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"不想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"偷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"然而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"如不偷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一刻","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不可","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"擁有","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"轉折句，表達不想偷情，但又無法擁有的矛盾心理。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0008","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0008","text":"是恨是悔疚 仍然有你 仍然愛你","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["情感","糾結","愛恨"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["恨","悔疚","仍然有","仍然愛"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,4,4,0,0,5,5,0,0,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["si6","han6","si6","fui3","gau3","jing4","jin4","jau5","nei5","jing4","jin4","oi3","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"恨","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"悔疚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"判斷句，表達複雜的情感，包含恨與愛、悔疚與擁有。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0009","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0009","text":"傷心也只好偷 永遠偷不夠","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["痛苦","偷情","不滿足"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["傷心","偷","永遠","偷不夠"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,5,9,9,3,5,5,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["soeng1","sam1","jaa5","zi2","hou2","tau1","wing5","jyun5","tau1","bat1","gau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"傷心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"只好","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"偷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"永遠","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"偷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不夠","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"判斷句，將傷心與偷情連結，再次強調慾望的不滿足。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0010","text":"斷絕以後還有 愛得深罪是永久 離開分手","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["後果","罪惡","永久"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["斷絕","愛得深","罪","永久","離開","分手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,5,2,0,5,4,3,3,2,2,5,9,0,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["dyun6","zyut6","ji5","hau6","waan4","jau5","oi3","dak1","sam1","zeoi6","si6","wing5","gau2","lei4","hoi1","fan1","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"斷絕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"以後","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"還有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"深罪","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"永久","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"離開","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"分手","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"判斷句，描述愛得越深，罪惡感越重，最終導致離開分手。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0011","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0011","text":"而然後不停回頭 再會時各覓藉口","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["回憶","逃避","藉口"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["回頭","再會","藉口"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,3,0,0,0,4,0,4,2,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji4","jin4","hau6","bat1","ting4","wui4","tau4","zoi3","si4","gok3","mik6","ze3","hau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"然後","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不停","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"回頭","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"再會","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"時","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"各","pos":"DET"},{"text":"覓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"藉口","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"判斷句，描述不斷回頭看，再見面時各自尋找藉口的心態。"},"source":{"title":"愛不到要偷","artists":["邰正宵"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5592","prev_line_id":"lyr_6YKw5q2j5a61_NTU5Mg_0010","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
